00:22:03.852 --> 00:22:07.772
That was very nice. I was really intrigued by the

367
00:22:07.812 --> 00:22:11.552
GDF15 data because I think that's a really

368
00:22:11.592 --> 00:22:13.672
important area of research

369
00:22:15.612 --> 00:22:19.432
with cachexia. The adipose tissue looked really

370
00:22:19.572 --> 00:22:19.872
good.

371
00:22:20.112 --> 00:22:21.112
Yes, yes.

372
00:22:21.252 --> 00:22:23.272
And

