00:23:29.212 --> 00:23:32.952
diet, they have this effect on the

397
00:23:32.992 --> 00:23:34.312
adipose tissue landscape?

398
00:23:35.112 --> 00:23:39.022
I have no idea. We don't even know whether it's a

