00:23:53.072 --> 00:23:53.332
Mm-hmm.

404
00:23:54.152 --> 00:23:54.652
You'll see-

405
00:23:55.132 --> 00:23:55.532
Less

406
00:23:55.752 --> 00:23:56.982
... weightless, and that's why the IL6 is there.

407
00:23:57.012 --> 00:23:57.182
Yes.

408
00:23:58.012 --> 00:24:01.912
So those experiments are ongoing right now. Yes.

409
00:24:05.612 --> 00:24:06.972
Hi, Karen. Great talk.

