440
00:25:53.572 --> 00:25:56.792
I have to say, I think that precision is the right word.

441
00:25:56.832 --> 00:25:59.912
I think it's going to be different for different tumors, different therapies-

442
00:25:59.972 --> 00:25:59.982
Mm

443
00:25:59.982 --> 00:26:00.872
... different patients.

444
00:26:01.122 --> 00:26:01.212
Mm.

445
00:26:01.232 --> 00:26:04.772
So there's not going to be a one-size-fits-all, you shouldn't eat sugar, you

446
00:26:04.832 --> 00:26:08.392
shouldn't eat serine. I think it's going to be really very context dependent.

447
00:26:08.712 --> 00:26:11.752
Right. The IDH wild type tumors may behave differently than-

448
00:26:11.812 --> 00:26:12.892
Exactly. Yes

449
00:26:12.902 --> 00:26:15.082
... IDH mutated. Right. And the second question is,

