1293
01:13:37.508 --> 01:13:41.408
pathways. And when we look at the microbial profiles between

1294
01:13:41.448 --> 01:13:44.608
the two subtypes, we see very different

1295
01:13:45.468 --> 01:13:46.988
profiles. So there's

1296
01:13:48.008 --> 01:13:50.848
no really consistent changes between the subtypes.

1297
01:13:51.288 --> 01:13:55.088
So the first and second column for

1298
01:13:55.188 --> 01:13:57.348
both the abundance and the prevalence.

1299
01:13:58.268 --> 01:14:02.048
And when we look at a prevalent serrated polyp versus

1300
01:14:02.088 --> 01:14:05.308
adenoma, again, we don't really see any consistent

1301
01:14:05.808 --> 01:14:09.108
changes between these two subtypes.

1302
01:14:10.268 --> 01:14:14.108
So this indicates that distinct microbial changes may

1303
01:14:14.188 --> 01:14:17.408
underlie the distinct molecular

1304
01:14:17.628 --> 01:14:19.528
