1305
01:14:20.688 --> 01:14:23.788
So when we look at individual microbes along this

1306
01:14:24.208 --> 01:14:27.828
polyp-CRC sequence, so this is a summary of the

1307
01:14:27.868 --> 01:14:28.788
results that

1308
01:14:29.888 --> 01:14:33.728
we generated. We can say in healthy controls, the

1309
01:14:33.768 --> 01:14:37.368
