01:14:51.148 --> 01:14:53.728
stage, we can identify some

1315
01:14:55.188 --> 01:14:58.088
microbes that have been associated with colon cancer.

1316
01:14:58.488 --> 01:15:02.088
And when we move on to the colon cancer stage, and the

1317
01:15:02.148 --> 01:15:04.308
individual microbes that are enriched

