1356
01:17:23.867 --> 01:17:26.748
patterns that have been associated with CRC.

1357
01:17:28.148 --> 01:17:31.668
And we can also see that the correlation pattern is

1358
01:17:31.728 --> 01:17:34.848
stronger among cases compared to controls.

1359
01:17:37.068 --> 01:17:37.248
So,

1360
01:17:38.088 --> 01:17:41.388
we saw similar results when we look at colon cancer

1361
01:17:41.448 --> 01:17:45.388
specifically. So we developed a CRC microbial

1362
01:17:45.448 --> 01:17:49.008
diet score by using the microbes that have been

1363
01:17:49.148 --> 01:17:51.708
associated with CRC as the outcome.

1364
01:17:52.188 --> 01:17:55.868
So basically, we want to identify a

1365
01:17:55.908 --> 01:17:59.628
combination of food groups that is

1366
01:18:00.068 --> 01:18:03.728
