01:20:05.596 --> 01:20:07.076
cope with the early

1401
01:20:08.296 --> 01:20:11.516
session. So when we look at our

1402
01:20:12.296 --> 01:20:15.916
cohort data, look at coffee drinking after colon cancer

1403
01:20:15.976 --> 01:20:19.756
diagnosis, we saw that coffee drinkers had a

1404
01:20:19.816 --> 01:20:23.436
substantially better survival compared to non-coffee drinkers.

1405
01:20:24.096 --> 01:20:28.056
So we assessed the coffee drinking after colon cancer diagnosis, and we

1406
01:20:28.116 --> 01:20:32.006
see this very strong inverse association, again,

1407
01:20:32.006 --> 01:20:34.736
