1415
01:21:01.616 --> 01:21:05.396
non-drinkers, the heavy coffee

1416
01:21:05.416 --> 01:21:08.936
drinkers had a much better survival

1417
01:21:09.196 --> 01:21:10.636
among colon cancer patients.

1418
01:21:12.336 --> 01:21:15.856
And based on this observational data, we are now conducting a

